{"tid":1165730,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"傳情慾片流出　姚子羚強調係受害者","createTime":"2019-05-22T03:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T05:32:24.000Z","uid":72009,"like":9,"dislike":135,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"91d636c53ba6030292faea0a7f648922342156a2","tid":1165730,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T03:52:48.000Z","msg":"無綫藝員姚子羚日前突爆出疑偷食夜店經理人夫Raymond，更一度傳出涉及四角戀，不過Raymond前妻蔡宛珊（Sarika）早於2017年已跟Raymond開始分居，今年初正式簽字離婚，證明姚子羚並非「第三者」。<br />\n<br />\n據知姚子羚早前提出分手，事有湊巧她與Raymond就流出床照，姚子羚覺得是有人刻意做出來，無非想影響她，對於盛傳兩人有情慾片流出，她斬釘截表示沒有跟Raymond影過任何情慾片，亦冇拍過AV，甚至冇赤裸與對方影過一張照片，她強調自己也是受害者。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190521/bkn-20190521121608614-0521_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190521%2Fbkn-20190521121608614-0521_00862_001.html&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TQOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=250f7eb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190521/bkn-20190521121608614-0521_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />朋友"},{"pid":"1b3c55d722ab6935be755a1cecc860528ba2fe22","tid":1165730,"uid":85557,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T03:54:45.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"cf385a146a1b3863c16d4db87c39ed7dbf021606","tid":1165730,"uid":35231,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T03:55:40.000Z","msg":"0"},{"pid":"2ffb15a43227cef0b90e84fc2780ae8b7d47e366","tid":1165730,"uid":172507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T03:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e214b46fcaecf35bbdccafc6a766250032aa96f6","tid":1165730,"uid":156376,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T03:56:50.000Z","msg":"片呢"},{"pid":"fde3b1658c348f2e66600f2d230f6edc41e86454","tid":1165730,"uid":169435,"like":8,"dislike":210,"score":